data.description: Escape to your own private oasis at 52757 CR 365, a  ranch-style home nestled in a picturesque country setting. This idyllic property boasts a waterfront view from a serene private pond, offering you the tranquility you crave. The spacious open floor layout provides ample room for relaxation and entertainment, while the basement adds extra versatility to suit your needs. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, there's plenty of space for the whole family to enjoy. Plus, the property includes a detached garage and barn, perfect for storing your vehicles and equipment. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to experience country living at its finest on 11.48 acres of pure bliss.
